						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						FROM fs_news

						ORDER BY  id DESC, ordering DESC

						FROM fs_news

						ORDER BY  id DESC, ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,10

						 LIMIT 10

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1
						  	 ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC 
						 LIMIT 10

						FROM fs_news
						WHERE alias <> 'apple-iphone-8-va-iphone-8-plus:-khung-may-cung-hon-50-nap-lung-kinh-chip-a11-bionic-camera-moi'
							AND category_id = 100
							AND published = 1
							 AND alias <> 'apple-iphone-8-va-iphone-8-plus:-khung-may-cung-hon-50-nap-lung-kinh-chip-a11-bionic-camera-moi' 
						ORDER BY  id DESC, ordering DESC

						ORDER BY  id DESC, ordering DESC

 SELECT id,name,description,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,description,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,description,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  WHERE ( category_id = 100 
						  	OR category_id_wrapper like '%,100,%' )
						  	AND published = 1
						  	 ORDER BY  ordering DESC, id DESC
						  LIMIT 0,3

						 LIMIT 1

 SELECT id,name,description,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,description,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%3%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10
